# Walkthrough: Đặc Tả Tab & DOCX Export Implementation

## Changes Made

### Physics Page (`de-thi-vatli.html`)

#### CSS Changes
- Removed `display: grid` from `.main-content` to prevent conflict with tab switching
- Added `tab-content` / `tab-content-grid` visibility system using `display: none !important` / `display: block !important`
- Added comprehensive Đặc tả tab styling: header, action buttons, specification table, responsive breakpoints

#### HTML Changes
- Updated `main-content` div to `class="main-content tab-content tab-content-grid active" id="content-cauhinh"`
- Added full Đặc tả tab HTML content (`id="content-dacta"`) with:
  - Header section with Vietnamese text (BẢN ĐẶC TẢ ĐỀ KIỂM TRA ĐỊNH KÌ)
  - Action buttons: "Chuyển sang tab Đề thi" and "Tải về .docx"
  - Complex 4-row header table (TT, Chủ đề, Nội dung, Yêu cầu cần đạt, 12 cognition columns, Tổng)
  - Dynamic tbody and tfoot for generated data
- Added `docx@8.5.0` and `FileSaver.js` CDN script includes

#### JavaScript Changes
- Replaced simple `initTabs()` with full `switchTab(tabName)` function that shows/hides tab content panels
- Added `generateSpecTable()` function that:
  - Reads configuration from the Cấu hình tab (questions, points, cognition percentages)
  - Distributes questions across selected topics evenly
  - Splits each topic's questions by cognition level (Biết/Hiểu/Vận dụng)
  - Generates footer rows (Tổng số câu, Tổng số điểm, Tỉ lệ %)
- Added `generateYeuCau(topic)` mapping Physics topic IDs to requirement descriptions
- Added `exportDactaToDocx()` function using docx.js library for Word document generation
- Added button event handlers for tab switching and docx download

---

### Math Page (`de-thi-toan.html`)
- Already had all CSS/HTML/JS changes applied from a previous session
- Fixed `generateYeuCau()` function: replaced Physics topic IDs with correct Math topic IDs (mệnh đề, bất phương trình, hàm số, etc.)

## Verification

- ✅ Tab switching works: Cấu hình content hides when Đặc tả is active
- ✅ Vietnamese diacritical marks display correctly in table headers and content
- ✅ Specification table populates with correct data from the configuration
- ✅ Footer rows show Tổng số câu, Tổng số điểm (= 10), Tỉ lệ % (= 100)
- ✅ Action buttons (Chuyển sang tab Đề thi, Tải về .docx) are visible and functional

